@PlateJohnny @kemkominfo https://t.co/OMrEfRAfrb
en_text:
Kominfo SDH reminded that there would be a loss of not listing PSE, the Ministry of Communication and Information had issued a statement by mentioning sanctions in stages, starting from the reprimand, administrative fine, then blocking.
@Platejohnny @kemkominfo https://t.co/omrefrafrb
